      "message": "cmake: compact generated data headers\n\nChange the raw and json data generators to emit concatenated byte string literals instead of per-element initializer lists.\n\nAdd MakeByteArray in span.h so raw headers stay compact while still exposing the same compile-time byte spans.\n\nThe hash checks added in the previous commit keep the embedded fixture contents pinned while this commit only changes their C++ representation.\n\nCo-authored-by: Fabian Jahr <fjahr@protonmail.com>",
